00:04:33,658 --> 00:05:02,872
clothing and all the rest of that that we might need and this safety safety presumably from financial collapse and he does this by following the Dharma and what we mean by the Dharma here of course the just and righteous king is the five precepts now if you think of the five precepts you know the first one is not to kill not to kill any being but I mean not to kill any human being

