so you can imagine if in this world right now every human being were to take that precept there would in fact be a little bit of a change in the world to some great degree so if somebody were to keep the precepts if this king or if our rulers were to keep the precepts then it would have an effect upon the whole society now this goes back to the Buddha's position that our

