36
00:05:47,608 --> 00:05:52,254
And this always comes from this basic understanding of no harm.

37
00:05:52,696 --> 00:05:54,819
That's your platform, no harm.

38
00:05:55,439 --> 00:06:03,572
And then from that platform, the positives arise, compassion, the love, friendship and so on and so forth.

39
00:06:04,261 --> 00:06:12,249
And that's what is meant here by the Dhamma, by this very wheel-turning monarch and the righteous ruler.

40
