Now, as opposed to that, he says, even so the Tathagata, the Arahant, the perfectly enlightened one, the just and the righteous king of the Dhamma, relying on the Dhamma, honoring the Dhamma, esteeming and respecting it, with the Dhamma as his standard, banner and sovereign,

41
00:06:32,610 --> 00:06:59,209
provides lawful protection shelter and safety safety in regard to action by body speech and mind so so now he's talking individually now talking about each individual although himself of course specifically as the fully self-enlightened one also taking the dharma so the buddha has a great respect for what he's discovered for the understandings that he's come to which are

42
