in regard to action by body, speech and mind is the one who turns the incomparable wheel of the dharma in accordance with the dharma only and that wheel of the dharma cannot be turned back by any ascetic or brahmin or by any deva or mara or brahma or by anyone in the world so that's the power of goodness I mean it's not always obvious in the world as we see it but eventually

53
00:09:13,936 --> 00:09:22,087
